text: Ugo Bonnet (born 17 September 1993) is a French professional footballer who plays as a forward for Rodez. ==Professional career== Bonnet is a youth product of Castelnau Le Crès FC, moved to the US for a year, then joined Rodez AF when he returned to France. He made his professional debut with Rodez in a 2–0 Ligue 2 win over AJ Auxerre on 26 July 2019, scoring in the first minute of the game. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:People from Aveyron Category:Association football forwards Category:French footballers Category:Rodez AF players Category:Ligue 2 players Category:Championnat National players Category:Championnat National 2 players
